    `python run_tests.py`

## BNF Grammar

```
expr : simple_expr (OR simple_expr)*

simple_expr : term (AND term)*

term : constraint
     | LPAREN expr RPAREN

constraint : variable relational_operator value

value : INTEGER
      | FLOAT
      | STRING
      | BOOL

variable: ID

relational_operator : ( EQ | NE | LT | LTE | GT | GTE )
```


